    • Method Detail

      • extractFromFile

        List<LinkedHashMap<String,String>> extractFromFile(byte[] bytes)
                                            throws HodErrorException
        Extract content from a CSV file into a JSON format using HP Haven on Demand using a token proxy provided by a TokenProxyService
        Parameters:
        bytes - The bytes of a file containing the data to be extracted.
        Returns:
        List of JSON objects stored as a LinkedHashMap with column names as keys and cell values as values.
        Throws:
        NullPointerException - If a TokenProxyService has not been defined
        HodAuthenticationFailedException - If the token associated with the token proxy has expired
        HodErrorException
